I noticed that FitViewport extends ScalingViewport while ExtendViewport extends Viewport. The difference might be due to using enum _fit_ in ExtendViewport:

``` java
        Vector2 scaled = Scaling.fit.apply(worldWidth, worldHeight, screenWidth, screenHeight);
```

In the FitViewport this is simply:

``` java
        Vector2 scaled = scaling.apply(getWorldWidth(), getWorldHeight(), screenWidth, screenHeight);
```
